    "response": "The four tribes have warred and traded since before the oldest troll's memory. The Forest Trolls track prey through the canopy and speak the language of birds. The River Trolls grow fat on fish and gold, building their wicker cities along the waterways. The Blood Trolls eat their enemies raw and use war as prayer. The Shadow Trolls hold congress with spirits that walk between worlds. Each tribe has its strengths, and each has its price.",
